name: Salem Sprint
description:
by pyjam.as

Latest version of the game is available here: http://salem.pyjam.as

Controls: Arrow keys and number keys.

Made using Godot, OpenAI Dall-E, Stable Diffusion, Aseprite, Photoshop, and Ableton Live.

The team:

  • Emil Norsker (programming)
  • Asbjørn Olling (programming & art)
  • Rasmus Malver (art)
  • Linus Hjalsted (art & music)
  • Jeppe Thorup Poulsen (programming)
